# Force LF line endings for all text content so sha256 hashes in manifest.json
# stay deterministic across platforms (Windows checkout + Linux CI must produce
# the same bytes). Without this, Windows clones with autocrlf=true rewrite
# level_*.json with CRLF on checkout, and a manifest regenerated on Windows
# would have different hashes than one regenerated on Linux CI.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.py text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
